org.cougaar.core.qos.metrics
Interface MetricNotificationQualifier

All Known Implementing Classes:
CredibilityQualifier, DeltaValueQualifier
public interface MetricNotificationQualifier

This API is used to specify a qualification on potential callbacks from the MetricsService subscriptions. By default subscribers to a given path are called back whenever the value at that path changes. Notification qualifiers can limit that, for instance to prevent callbacks when the delta is too small or the credibility is too low.

Method Summary
 boolean shouldNotify(Metric metric)
          Decides whether the given metric, which would ordinarily be sent to subscribers through a callback, really should be propagated.
